cloud\\.claude\\logs\\claude_exec-1773785363572-76yhqe_2026-03-17T22-09-23-572Z.log:58:[Omitted long matching line]\nC:\\Users\\kazda\\kiro\\personas-cloud\\.claude\\commands\\idea-392b930f-audit-record-swallows-write-fa.md:15:AuditLog.record() catches database write errors and only emits a warn-level log. For a compliance audit log, a failed write means an audit trail gap. The method should throw or emit an alert, and at minimum escalate to error-level logging with the full entry payload so the gap is detectable.\nC:\\Users\\kazda\\kiro\\personas-cloud\\packages\\orchestrator\\src\\dispatcher.ts:273:      this.auditLog?.record({ action: 'key:decrypt', tenantId, resourceType: 'credential', resourceId });\nC:\\Users\\kazda\\kiro\\personas-cloud\\packages\\orchestrator\\src\\dispatcher.ts:278:      this.auditLog?.record({ action: 'key:decrypt_failed', tenantId, resourceType: 'credential', resourceId, detail: reason });\nC:\\Users\\kazda\\kiro\\personas-cloud\\packages\\orchestrator\\src\\httpApi.ts:154:        auditLog?.record({ action: 'key:encrypt', tenantId: body.projectId || ctx.projectId || 'default', resourceType: 'credential', resourceId: cred.id });\nC:\\Users\\kazda\\kiro\\personas-cloud\\.claude\\logs\\claude_exec-1773785860833-umeu58_2026-03-17T22-17-40-833Z.log:26:[Omitted long matching line]\nC:\\Users\\kazda\\kiro\\personas-cloud\\.claude\\logs\\claude_exec-1773785860833-umeu58_2026-03-17T22-17-40-833Z.log:37:[Omitted long matching line]\nC:\\Users\\kazda\\kiro\\personas-cloud\\.claude\\logs\\claude_exec-1773785860833-umeu58_2026-03-17T22-17-40-833Z.log:38:[Omitted long matching line]\nC:\\Users\\kazda\\kiro\\personas-cloud\\.claude\\logs\\claude_exec-1773786075299-mmuuvs_2026-03-17T22-21-15-299Z.log:19:[Omitted long matching line]\nC:\\Users\\kazda\\kiro\\personas-cloud\\.claude\\logs\\claude_exec-1773788753773-x2mxt3_2026-03-17T23-05-53-773Z.log:49:[Omitted long matching line]\nC:\\Users\\kazda\\kiro\\personas-cloud\\.claude\\logs\\claude_exec-17737893